org.redisson

Class Redisson

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.redisson.Redisson
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RedissonClient

    public class Redisson
extends Object
implements RedissonClient
    Main infrastructure class allows to get access to all Redisson objects on top of Redis server.
    Author:
    Nikita Koksharov
